- Keep API documentation up to date

Rule 2: Technical Documentation
- Document system architecture and data flow
- Maintain deployment guides and setup instructions
- Keep troubleshooting guides current
- Document configuration options and environment variables

Rule 3: User Documentation
- Provide clear user guides for platform features
- Document API endpoints with examples
- Maintain FAQ sections for common issues
- Keep documentation synchronized with code changes

